Package: tmapverse
Type: Package
Title: The Meta-Package for Thematic Mapping with 'tmap'
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
	person("Martijn", "Tennekes", , "mtennekes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("Olivier", "Roy", role = "ctb"))
Description: The 'tmapverse' package attaches a set of packages that are 
    commonly used for spatial plotting with 'tmap'. It includes 'tmap' and its 
    extensions ('tmap.glyphs', 'tmap.networks', 'tmap.cartogram', 'tmap.mapgl'), as well as 
    supporting spatial data packages ('sf', 'stars', 'terra'), and 'cols4all' for 
    exploring color palettes. The 
    package is intended for use in thematic mapping workflows and does not 
    include the full set of packages from the R-spatial ecosystem.
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
	tmap (>= 4.2),
	tmap.glyphs,
	tmap.networks,
	tmap.cartogram,
    tmap.mapgl,
	sf,
	stars,
	terra,
	cols4all,
	cli,
	crayon
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
